data.description: Is this your new home? Come take a look! This darling 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom all-brick home offers close to 1500sf, a converted garage as additional living space, nearly half an acre with fencing surrounding the front and back yard, as well as plenty of storage from a large shed and attic space. This property embraces a spacious floor plan, features a sizable kitchen with an island, fresh paint throughout, and no HOA just to name a few. The home is situated in a convenient, quiet neighborhood with outstanding schools nearby and is an easy commute to military bases, beaches and shopping. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own!
